    See if the incoming num is in the range of [local min, s.top()]
    T:O(n)/S:O(n)
    FAIL case: [3,5,0,3,4]
    -----
    AC, record every ascending region and binary search on these regions
    T(n) = log1 + ... + log(n/2) = O(nlogn)
    S: O(n)
*/
class Solution {
public:
